      <span class="label-pill">Features in depth</span>
      <h2 class="h-lg">Every major <span class="accent">Ubersuggest feature</span>, tested.</h2>
      <p>What's actually in the box — and where each feature lands when you need it for real work.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ba-grid">
      <div class="ba-col after" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">01</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Keyword research</h4>
              <p>The strongest feature. 5,325+ suggestions per seed term, 83% volume accuracy, questions and comparison keywords included. The difficulty scores skew low, so treat them directionally — but the sheer volume of keyword ideas is genuinely useful for content planning.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">02</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Site audit</h4>
              <p>Crawls your site and surfaces technical SEO issues: missing meta tags, broken links, duplicate content, slow pages. Works well for sites up to a few hundred pages. Not as deep as Screaming Frog or DeepCrawl, but actionable for small businesses.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">03</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Backlink analysis</h4>
              <p>Shows inbound links and domain authority scores. The database is 60–70% smaller than Ahrefs — useful for high-level checks, not for serious link-building campaigns where missing data costs you opportunities.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">04</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Rank tracking</h4>
              <p>Tracks keyword positions daily across all paid plans. You can track by city and ZIP code for local queries. One of the better rank tracking implementations at this price point — the daily updates are legitimately useful.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">05</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Content ideas and article outlines</h4>
              <p>Shows what's ranking for a topic, with estimated traffic and social shares. Generates basic article outlines based on top results. Useful for content ideation — but you still write everything. No drafts, no publishing.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">06</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Chrome extension</h4>
              <p>The free Chrome extension gives 40 searches per day with keyword volume, CPC, and competition data in Google search results. The most useful free tier in the category for casual research.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">07</span>
            <div>
              <h4>What's missing</h4>
              <p>API access, Zapier integration, content writing or publishing, Google Business Profile tools, and accurate traffic estimates for competitive analysis. The data floor is real — know it before you buy.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PRICING -->
  <section class="cost-section">
    <div class="cost-header">
      <span class="label-pill">Pricing</span>
      <h2 class="h-lg">What Ubersuggest <span class="accent">actually costs.</span></h2>
      <p>Three monthly tiers, no annual discount, and a lifetime deal that's worth doing the math on. The 7-day free trial plus 30-day money-back guarantee makes it relatively low risk to test.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="cost-table">
      <div class="cost-row head">
        <div class="cost-cell head-cell">Tier</div>
        <div class="cost-cell head-cell">Ubersuggest</div>
        <div class="cost-cell head-cell">Best fit</div>
        <div class="cost-cell head-cell brand">theStacc equivalent</div>
      </div>
      <div class="cost-row">
        <div class="cost-cell label"><div class="vert">Individual</div><div class="price" style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;">1 project · 125 keywords</div></div>
        <div class="cost-cell"><div class="price">$29</div><div class="per">per month</div></div>
        <div class="cost-cell"><div class="price" style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;">Solo blogger, small biz owner</div></div>
        <div class="cost-cell brand"><div class="price brand">$49</div><div class="per">starter · all-in</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="cost-row">
        <div class="cost-cell label"><div class="vert">Business</div><div class="price" style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;">7 projects · 1,050 keywords</div></div>
        <div class="cost-cell"><div class="price">$49</div><div class="per">per month</div></div>
        <div class="cost-cell"><div class="price" style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;">Small agencies, consultants</div></div>
        <div class="cost-cell brand"><div class="price brand">$99</div><div class="per">pro · all-in</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="cost-row">
        <div class="cost-cell label"><div class="vert">Enterprise</div><div class="price" style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;">15 projects · 4,500 keywords</div></div>
