        <div class="cost-cell brand"><div class="price brand">$199</div><div class="per">scale · all-in</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="cost-savings">
        <div class="big">Ubersuggest gives you data. theStacc gives you published content.</div>
        <div class="lbl">Different tools for different jobs — most small businesses need the second one.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="cost-footnote">*Ubersuggest lifetime deal: approximately $290 (Individual), $490 (Business), $990 (Enterprise) as a one-time payment. Pricing varies by promotion. 7-day free trial available. No annual billing option.</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHO IT'S FOR -->
  <section class="problem-section">
    <div class="problem-header">
      <span class="label-pill">Who it's for</span>
      <h2 class="h-lg">Who should buy Ubersuggest — <span class="accent">and who shouldn't.</span></h2>
      <p>The clearest filter: how much SEO data accuracy do you actually need?</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ba-grid">
      <div class="ba-col after">
        <div class="ba-head">
          <span class="ba-label">Buy Ubersuggest if</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">You're a beginner or budget-constrained operator.</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">Three signals Ubersuggest is the right fit.</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>You're new to SEO and need an approachable starting point</h4><p>Clean UI, no overwhelming data tables, solid keyword suggestions. The best on-ramp in the category at this price.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>You want to eliminate recurring software costs with a lifetime deal</h4><p>The $290–$990 one-time payment pays back in under a year for consistent users.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>You're in a low-to-medium competition niche</h4><p>Where 83% keyword volume accuracy is good enough to build a content plan and the directional difficulty scores don't lead you astray.</p></div></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="ba-col before">
        <div class="ba-head">
          <span class="ba-label">Skip Ubersuggest if</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">You need accurate competitive data or content publishing.</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">Three signals another tool fits better.</p>
