      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What is Ubersuggest?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">An all-in-one SEO platform acquired by Neil Patel in 2017 that provides keyword research, site audits, backlink analysis, rank tracking, and content ideas. Built for beginners and small businesses who need professional SEO data without paying for Ahrefs or Semrush.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How much does Ubersuggest cost?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">$29/month (Individual), $49/month (Business), $99/month (Enterprise) on monthly billing. No annual discount option. Lifetime deal available for approximately $290–$990 one-time depending on tier and current promotions. 7-day free trial with 30-day money-back guarantee.</div>
