        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Is Ubersuggest's data accurate?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Keyword volume accuracy is 83% in independent testing — solid. Traffic estimates are only 50.1% accurate, making them directional at best. Keyword difficulty scores consistently skew low compared to Ahrefs and Semrush. Know this going in.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Is the Ubersuggest lifetime deal worth it?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">For beginners planning long-term use, yes — the $290–$990 one-time payment pays back in under a year and eliminates the monthly subscription forever. For users likely to outgrow the tool quickly, monthly billing is the safer option.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Does Ubersuggest write content for you?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">No. Ubersuggest surfaces keyword ideas and content outlines based on top-ranking pages. You write, edit, and publish every piece of content yourself. If you need done-for-you publishing, theStacc handles it for $99/month.</div>
