        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Can Ubersuggest replace Ahrefs or Semrush?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">For basic keyword research and site audits, yes. For advanced backlink analysis, competitive intelligence, API access, and enterprise reporting — no. The data gaps are real and matter in competitive niches.</div>
